* Personal finance tracking is essential for
managing expenses effectively.

* Many people struggle with overspending due
to lack of proper monitoring.

* This project provides a Python-based Budget
Management Tool using Tkinter GUI, file
handling, and data visualization.

A Budget Management Tool is needed to:
-> Track daily expenses
-> Categorize spending
-> Generate visual reports
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Existing Systems :
Current Financial Tracking Methods are like ,
* Manual Tracking (Notebooks/Spreadsheets):
  -> Users manually enter expenses.
  -> Prone to errors and lacks automation.
* Bank Statements & Apps
    -> Mobile banking apps provide spending insights.
    -> No offline access or customizable budgeting.
* Standalone Expense Tracking Apps
   -> Require subscriptions or internet access.
   -> Data security concerns with third-party apps. 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
List of Python Libraries Used :
1. Tkinter/ttk  -> Builds offline GUI (buttons, inputs, tables)
2. Pandas ->  Manages expense data (CSV read/write, categorization)
3. Matplotlib ->  Generates visual reports (pie charts, trends)
4. OS ->  Handles local file storage (no cloud needed)
================================================================================================================================================================================================================
